name: W H A V E S.001
description: Whaves are kinetic orbs of energy provisioned by the Gods of Edah and scattered across the universe. They power the Achilia portals which allow H=n’ots to travel across parallel dimensions in time and space. The bravest of travelers collect whave orbs to open the portals and commence their journey throughout Edah. Travelers who collect sets of orbs will be gifted an Achilia portal to add to their collection; portal shapes are different depending on the set of whaves the traveler holds. Ak’hala tikém (peace be with you traveler)
